# Clerk publishable key for the homepage's client-side authentication.
#
# This is a PUBLIC key (it is meant to ship in the browser bundle). The Clerk
# secret key is never used here: the site is a static export with no server.
#
# Local development:
#   Copy this file to `.env.local` (git-ignored) and paste your Clerk
#   *development* publishable key from the Clerk Dashboard (API Keys).
#
# Production:
#   Do not commit the production key. Set it as a GitHub Actions repository
#   *Variable* named NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY so the deploy build
#   bakes it in. See setup.md -> "Add Login and Sign Up With Clerk".
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
